body: It is a far, far better thing that I do, than I have ever done; it is a far, far better rest I go to than I have ever known. - a tale of two cities
SELECT * FROM posts p left join users added on added.id=p.added_by left join users posted on posted.id=p.user_to left join interest i on i.id=p.interest_id having p.added_by=2
